Detailed Description

cvmx_led_prt_fmt

LED_PRT_FMT = LED Port Status Infomation Format

Notes: TX: RGMII TX block is sending packet data or extends on the port RX: RGMII RX block has received non-idle cycle

For short transfers, LEDs will remain on for at least one blink cycle
